column16: This conflict was foreordained, you know. All is laid out upon the Wheel of Fate, free from the meddling hands of mortals.
column17: Ah...yesss... So <Emphasis>this</Emphasis> is the Dark! I am becoming one with you now... It is... It is ecstasy! Yes! The Dark has chosen me! The bodies of the unwitting will be my vessels! I am immortal...

column16: We'll soon be off to our next destination! Raise your rods and make ready to set sail!
column17: Seems nature doesn't feel like welcoming us to the Rhotano Sea! No matter─we'll take what we need!
